title: Eastpak provider checked pink
description_long:
Grab-and-go! Featuring two main roomy compartments and a padded laptop sleeve for optimal security, the Eastpak Provider will become your most reliable mate. Especially designed to host all your gear and techy kits, this backpack provides super convenience thanks to its little extras that will help you keep organized, such as the ultimate key keeper, a perfect accessory for energetic users!
Make the most out of the Eastpak Provider, available in a wide variety of urban colours and patterns!

title: Eastpak provider chechbook black
description:
• Laptop sleeve 38 x 29 x 5cm
  • Two large compartments including padded laptop sleeve
  • Padded bottom
  • Front organizer pocket with detachable key keeper
  • Comfortable quilted padded back
  • Thick padded shoulder straps with SGS
  • Side compression straps
  • Rubber molded handle
description_long: Two spacious compartments and a padded laptop sleeve provide ample room for all your tech - the Eastpak Provider backpack is a great way to get your stuff around. It’s a very comfortable fit with extra features like the key keeper to help you stay organised, and it’s a great-looking accessory! The Eastpak Provider backpack comes in a great range of alternate colours and designs

title: Eastpak kentukey smartuals navy
description_long: It fits the bill in both function and elegance! This shoulder bag accommodates all your devices, folders, books and essentials, while its adjustable strap offers optimal convenience. Stylish, easy to carry and absolutely practical, it disposes of a multitude of pockets to keep your stuff organised, no matter the task. Outstanding in every sense of the word!
